</table>
<p><br />For more information, please visit:<br /><a href="http://wiki.openelec.tv/index.php/Migrating_to_Another_Build" target="_blank">http://wiki.openelec.tv/index.php/Migrating_to_Another_Build</a></p>
<p> </p>
<h3>Thank You!</h3>
<p>We would like to thank our users, team members and partners for testing, reporting and fixing issues, creating how-to documents, developing new features, and their <a href="/donate" target="_blank">donations of hardware and funds</a> to the project. We appreciate your continued support, without it we would not be able to continue.</p>
<p> </p>
